docs.lead_paragraph: MAINE INSANE ASYLUM. On the 30th November 1853, there were 119 patients; admitted during the year, 110 of whom 57 were males and and 53 females--making 229 under treatment, 118 males and 111 females, Of these there have been discharged 114, received 49, improved 15, unimporved 18, and 32 have died--16 males and 16 females.
